":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:18:09.000Z","msg":"然而有幾多個係真好人，坐喺人地個位唔會腐化行惡。<br />\n<br />\n世界唔係得好人壞人，重有時而行善，時而行惡，有私欲嘅普通人。"},{"pid":"2abaffa8f27ffece7f8fad85631bffdac31021e9","tid":1058977,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:30:58.000Z","msg":"幾時到689"},{"pid":"9dd8dadb07590b3f3bec2312f25614dde0d268c1","tid":1058977,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:33:49.000Z","msg":"李怡 先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96d85912080d3e76ddfe063ce10329b9d473e35","tid":1058977,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a9dab54efbbb2288ec840478d20db422ea5016e","tid":1058977,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"報應用係依度 合理好多 一直覺得報應依個字太自我安慰"},{"pid":"0ab18e2d4e853362097cb3e882786d73ae215c9f","tid":1058977,"uid":240606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"封肛大葬"},{"pid":"6e1f9e065f96dbdd157ca70e8c591ee2f39b95a3","tid":1058977,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"呢個時候望都望入去坐啦<br />\n出番嚟你可能仲凶險呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf75e37b29a8e509dda8b209804d2323151b8485","tid":1058977,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"其實李怡寫呢篇文都好無奈"},{"pid":"bb17f8ee95c78cec982858b6694a7473b6da9b40","tid":1058977,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:55:41.000Z","msg":"講得好 <br />\n<br />\n奶共狗死不足惜"}]}